Author: GitHub
Description:
This week on The Download, Cassidy covers the release of Git 2.52 and its new "jetpack" feature for checking file history. We also dive into the launch of Google's Gemini 3 Pro model in GitHub Copilot and Microsoft's new Agent 365 for the enterprise. Plus, we spotlight VERT, a privacy-focused open source file converter.

#Git #GitHub #Gemini #OpenSource
